dc_title_s: Map of the Little Scioto River and Pine Creek Basins and adjacent Ohio River tributaries showing availability of underground water
dc_description_s: Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the Little Scioto River and Pine Creek Basins and adjacent Ohio River tributaries and quality of underground water.|Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.|"Prepared by HENRY L. PREE, JR., Geologist, Ohio Division of Water"|Scale bar lower right corner of map.
